gement-2-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"fleet-management-2\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-309\" />','Fleet Management','','publish','open','open','','fleet-management','','','2014-06-26 18:25:35','2014-06-26 18:25:35','',109,'http://localhost:8888/?page_id=115',0,'page','',0),(116,1,'2014-06-26 16:03:22','2014-06-26 16:03:22','','Fleet Management','','inherit','open','open','','115-revision-v1','','','2014-06-26 16:03:22','2014-06-26 16:03:22','',115,'http://localhost:8888/?p=116',0,'revision','',0),(117,1,'2014-06-26 16:03:36','2014-06-26 16:03:36','<h2 style=\"color: #000000;\">Caterpillar Certified Rebuild</h2>\r\nFoley, Inc.\'s Certified Rebuild program takes advantage of the fact that Cat equipment is built to be rebuilt for a second life. The end result is a like-new machine with the latest technology and engineering updates, complete with a new warranty and Serial number-all at a fraction of the cost of a new machine.\r\n\r\n<a style=\"color: #336699;\" title=\"Certified REbuild\" href=\"http://www.foleyinc.com/assets/uploads/Certified%20Rebuild%20Brochure.pdf\">Certified Rebuild Information</a>\r\n\r\nBesides improving your environmental profile, Cat Certified Rebuilds come with the following advantages:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Every component - down to the frame and wiring harnesses - is restored to like-new condition or replaced</li>\r\n	<li>7,000 parts are repaired, replaced or reconditioned in total machine rebuilds</li>\r\n	<li>More than 350 tests or inspections are performed</li>\r\n	<li>The machine is completely repainted and new graphics are applied on a total-machine rebuild</li>\r\n	<li>Emission upgrades are also available.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>\r\nAlso, maximize the built-in value of your power train...\r\n\r\n</strong>\r\n\r\nFoley, Inc.\'s Caterpillar Certified Power Train Rebuild Program offers a second life for your Cat Construction Power Train. For maximum productivity, improved reliability and availability, this is a 